summary: A brief email chain from August 29, 2019, regarding the forwarding of information about 'Epstein calls' among team members. The document shows internal communication about ensuring receipt of previous call records.
keyFacts: Email communication dated August 29, 2019, references 'Epstein calls'.
The sender is forwarding call information to ensure a team has received 'all of these previous calls'.
The document indicates internal team coordination regarding Epstein-related call records.
